<emphasis id="B970EAFEFFFFF6118BA135C3FBCAFE67" bold="true" box="[703,1135,479,508]" pageId="59" pageNumber="117">Subspecies and Distribution.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BBB36ECFFFFF6118BC1361EFC87FD7C" blockId="59.[703,1329,282,704]" lastBlockId="59.[117,1329,710,2521]" pageId="59" pageNumber="117">
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFFFF6118BC1361EFC87FD7C" authority="Bergmans, 2001" authorityName="Bergmans" authorityYear="2001" baseAuthorityName="Bergmans" baseAuthorityYear="2001" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Paranyctimene" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="59" pageNumber="117" phylum="Chordata" rank="subSpecies" species="tenax" subSpecies="tenax">P.t.tenaxBergmans,2001—presumablymuchofNewGuinea(possiblyfoundpri-marilyinSlowlands);distributionallimitsbetweenthisspeciesandtheUnstripedTube-noseFruitBat(FP.raptor)areuncer-tainandthusdistributiongivenhereistentative.</taxonomicName>
